node.title: Victoria has recorded 1,365 new local COVID-19 cases and nine deaths
node.alt: Shoppers both seated and walking in a Melbourne arcade with a Christmas tree in the background.
node.description: There are now 14,383 active cases of the virus in Victoria, and 547 people have died during the current Delta outbreak.
node.content:
["Victoria has recorded 1,365\u00a0new local COVID-19 cases and nine\u00a0deaths.", "There are now 14,383 active cases of the virus in Victoria, and 547\u00a0people have died during the current Delta outbreak.", "There are 288 people in hospital with COVID-19, of whom 44\u00a0are in intensive care and 20\u00a0are on a ventilator.", "The new cases were detected from 67,545\u00a0test results received yesterday.", "There were 4,094 doses of vaccine administered at state-run sites yesterday, as well as more vaccinations at GP clinics and other venues.", "More to come.", "", "
Heavily mutated Omicron variant puts scientist on alert
"]
